4. **PO partial delivery progress bars** — Visual nicety, not a blocker
5. **Supplier WhatsApp click-to-chat** — Store has the phone number; `wa.me` link is 10 minutes work but not a V1 blocker
6. **Multi-currency** — Single-store India shop uses ₹ only
7. **Product batch/lot tracking** — Enterprise feature, out of scope
8. **Automatic scheduled backup** — localStorage has no background task capability; manual export is sufficient for V1
9. **Dashboard profit trend chart** — Revenue chart exists; adding profit trend before fixing the profit calculation itself would show wrong data anyway
10. **Advanced analytics filters** — Time range is already solid (Today/Week/Month/Quarter/Year/Custom); more filters add complexity without proportional value

